UserSessionDTO Data Type

Class for transferring information about the currently logged in user.

Properties
name data type description
orgs array of SessionOrgInfoDTO
user_id number
user_fname string
user_lname string
user_email string
is_saml boolean
saml_alias string
csrf_token string
session_ip string
is_ldap boolean
